将重新在arXiv上发布。此外，其团队制造的LK-99室温超导材料或许可以在一个月之内被复制，其成员也会对LK-99的制作方法进行指导，在文章中公开LK-99的制作方法，也正是为了接受各方的质疑。（每日经济新闻） 独家 | 韩国“全球首个室温超导体”科学家团队成员回应：LK-99或可在一个月内被复制，公开制作方法是为了接受质疑"},"attached_info":"Cj8Inua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk4OTEzMzY1IJv8nKYGMAA41gJAAXIJNjE0ODQ5NTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"554 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e1c1d70e144a3a605018432c3c9c9916_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1690809656.546800","card_id":"Q_607961712","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":607961712,"title":"封神里纣王害了那么多忠臣，为什么唯独对闻太师尊重有加?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/607961712","type":"question","created":1687393589,"answer_count":49,"follower_count":69,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,5823,34991,44081,176813],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Inua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk3MzgzMTQ3ILWqzqQGMAA4RUACcgk2MDc5NjE3MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"179 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1690809656.547268","card_id":"Q_614845058","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":614845058,"title":"泽连斯基在社交媒体表示「战争正逐渐回到俄罗斯境内 」，当前俄乌战况如何，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/614845058","type":"question","created":1690775532,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":48,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://