img.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3252,6756,6838,404175],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"学硕要“退场”了吗？近年来，随着研究生持续扩招，这一问题被反复热议。公众对于“人才过剩”的敏感神经，似乎开始集中在学术型硕士身上。日前，西南大学经济管理学院发布公告，从2024级开始，不再招收统计学专业（专业代码020208）硕士研究生。此外，中国科学技术大学和西北工业大学也在近期宣布，不再招收软件工程学术学位硕士研究生。东北林业大学的风景园林学、公共管理学两个学硕专业也从2024年起停止招生。学硕不断缩招，甚至停招，已经成了近几年的趋势。反之，在规模上，专硕开始“做大做强”。作为硕士研究生教育的两种不同类型，学硕和专硕各有其特点和培养目标。但事实上，长期以来，对于专硕的培养模式、培养目标一直存在争议。甚至有观点认为，专硕是低配版、短学制的学硕。学硕“停招”？"},"attached_info":"ClUInua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk4NzMyMTg1IKGMgqYGMAA44gJAHHIJNjE0MDMzNDE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/cf6b126ef_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1690809656.569475","card_id":"Q_614143988","target":{"id":614143988,"title":"如何评价动画《雾山五行》第二季「犀川幻紫林篇」第一集？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/614143988","type":"question","created":1690376299,"answer_count":43,"follower_count":105,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[128,15840,222096,598265,1723815],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"第二季终于开播了！！！"},"attached_info":"ClQInua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk4NzU2NjY3IOuwhKYGMAA4aUAdcgk2MTQxNDM5ODh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4d1fd1e8279233b2982a3061364dae15_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1690809656.569884","card_id":"Q_614877060","target":{"id":614877060,"title":"2023 年女足世界杯日本 4:0 西班牙，全场控球率仅 23%，三战全胜头名出线，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/614877060","type":"question","created":1690793858,"answer_count":47,"follower_count":101,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","n