「村戏」，什么样？"},"attached_info":"ClUInua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk4NjU3MDU4IK/V+KUGMAA48gFAIXIJNjEzNjk1NTIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-429e334f478795cf9008afe1f710666a_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1690809656.574313","card_id":"Q_614117765","target":{"id":614117765,"title":"如果走进一座核电站，你会对什么最好奇？最想看的地方是哪里？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/614117765","type":"question","created":1690368972,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":52,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[458,5304,9085,42753,137155],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"8月13日-19日，我们将开启为期一周的「核能之旅」，现邀请2名知乎用户，到访福建福清核电站以及成都两个核机构，近距离了解我国核能发展以及相关知识，与专业人员讨论。 「核能之旅」期间，我们将同步推出所见所闻。你会对什么最好奇？最想看的地方是哪里？欢迎大家来聊聊你对核能最好奇的问题，届时我们将整理大家的“好奇点”、“关注点”，逐一探访揭秘。 赶紧来加入我们吧！也欢迎大家发布想法与我们互动！发布想法时记得要加＃前方核能＃标签哦~~~ 具体如何加入我们，请点击想法链接→→→中国核工业集团有限公司的想法 - 知乎 https://www.zhihu.com/pin/1667578857388605441"},"attached_info":"ClQInua7/eyinJghEAMaCDk4NzUwODQ2IMz3g6YGMAA4NEAicgk2MTQxMTc3NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f6b78f10daceb2eeb53437fd899210ae_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"35_1690809656.575535","card_id":"Q_605103249","target":{"id":605103249,"title":"你会存钱吗？为什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/605103249","type":"question","created":1686041352,"answer_count":198,"follower_count":226,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1837,158098,166868],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,